{"tid":501732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(猜猜我是誰) 無懼冷鋒 「港姐人妻」越南大解放 網民話﹕呢個阿媽真...火","createTime":"2017-12-17T06:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T14:40:26.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e958d2443e90ac7b12f02278bb335782e1778c87","tid":501732,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"冷鋒殺到，天文台噚日發出入冬後首個寒冷天氣警告，今日市區氣溫最低只有12℃。<br />\n<br />\n為咗避寒，唔少藝人都會走轉熱帶地方，好似2012年港姐冠軍張名雅，近日又同老公去旅行，今次揀咗越南。<br />\n<br />\n張名雅自從去年同律師男友蔡錦豪（Joe）結婚後，生咗囝囝Mario，佢經常會喺社交網晒吓自己有幾幸福，當然唔少得就係晒身材啦，有時真係閃到呢......。張名雅噚日係ig限時動態show咗比堅尼照，見佢不時口張開，個樣非常誘人，而身材比起未生之前更為豐滿，有網友留言﹕「呢個阿媽真...火。」應該係話好惹火啦，難得老公都唔介意太太咁show off，真係羨慕死人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145758_af35d9f39c23b9f511148bf76db56343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145758_af35d9f39c23b9f511148bf76db56343.jpg&h=2e1c4da5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145758_a18e70549f7e328b91bfcfe56386e575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145758_a18e70549f7e328b91bfcfe56386e575.jpg&h=e43e9cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145759_d1c5d20c8998bc942ec66aa3bd123e59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145759_d1c5d20c8998bc942ec66aa3bd123e59.jpg&h=5d2cf327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145759_f1214c7cb2139370324935479071e376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145759_f1214c7cb2139370324935479071e376.jpg&h=f88e7796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171217/57591899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57591899&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=cb4d8ca0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57591899&h=bae31955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171217/57591899</a>"},{"pid":"548a721f437688557d6d0034c40e758e601838c2","tid":501732,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"佢戴錯罩呀？"},{"pid":"3d1e79d3d9ef1cc0931302316c38c1eafc039ee6","tid":501732,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢戴錯罩呀？</blockquote><br />\n港女興帶大兩個cup扮大包米"},{"pid":"71401e392e9a0c9307e3fb6a85b06047966d41ea","tid":501732,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"離撚哂罩 想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7adcd2a2cbe3fef28eb4637d287b36eb9f5608","tid":501732,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5f3b3f8576356684368ae677e88ac74022e8ccb","tid":501732,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"件泳衣買錯size?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}